     H            Y.
     F** AL#R75 **************************************
     F*仕切りにページトータルセット                *
     F*        ITS.         2015.05.27               *
     F************************************************
     FAL#WP73 UF  F    0256            DISK
      *
     IAL#WP73 AA  01
     I                                        1 256 IALL
     I                                        1   1 IDTK
     I                                        8  100IPAG#
     I                                       11  130IPAGT
      *
     I            DS
     I                                        1   80WKHZ
     I                                        1   40WKYY
     I                                        5   60WKMM
     I                                        7   80WKDD
      *
     I            DS
     I                                        1  140WTIME
     I                                        1   60STIME
     I                                        7  140SDATE
      *
     I           SDS
     I                                     *PROGRAM W$PGM
     I                                      244 253 W$WSID
     I                                      254 263 @@USER
     I                                      264 269 W$JBNO
      *----------------------------------------------------*
      * PLIST                                              *
      *----------------------------------------------------*
      *----------------------------------------------------*
      *   K  E  Y   L I  S  T                              *
      *----------------------------------------------------*
      *ページトータルをセット
     C                     TIME           WTIME
     C                     Z-ADD0         WKPAGT  30
     C                     Z-ADD0         WKPAG#  30
      *
      *仕切りの枚数をカウント
     C           *HIVAL    SETGTAL#WP73
     C                     READPAL#WP73                  22
     C           *IN22     DOWEQ'0'
     C           IDTK      IFEQ '3'
     C                     ADD  1         WKPAGT
     C                     ENDIF
     C                     READPAL#WP73                  22
     C                     ENDDO
      *
     C                     Z-ADDWKPAGT    WKPAG#
     C*********            Z-ADD0         WKPAG#
     C           *HIVAL    SETGTAL#WP73
     C                     READPAL#WP73                  22
     C           *IN22     DOWEQ'0'
     C           IDTK      IFEQ '3'
     C***********          ADD  1         WKPAG#
     C                     EXCPTDT
     C                     SUB  1         WKPAG#
     C                     ENDIF
     C                     READPAL#WP73                  22
     C                     ENDDO
      *
     C                     SETON                     LR
     C                     RETRN
     OAL#WP73 E                DT
     O                         WKPAG#    11
     O                         WKPAGT    14
